title: Sample Book, Dessins Nouveauté, 1926–27
description: Selection of designs with the strong colors and contrasts of the mid-twenties with examples of large bold design and small figured patterns. Samples are bound in boards. Gilt lettering. The dark papers have been dyed (rongeant).

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Dessins Nouveauté, 1926–27; Manufactured by Gillet et Fils ; France; block-printed and dyed; H x W: 16.5 x 24.5 cm (6 1/2 x 9 5/8 in.); Gift of Martin Fabrics Corporation; 1951-163-1-1/156
